title: Weds Post Show – Cinco De Mayo! (5-5-21)
itunes:title: Weds Post Show – Cinco De Mayo! (5-5-21)
description:
Bobby decided to put on two interviews with affiliates about BobbyFest. It's a look behind the scenes! He also talks about an underrated Brooks + Dunn song. Two crazy stories: One about a woman who snuck a gun into jail and the 2nd about a woman who got 2 holes in one within minutes! Bobby gets interviewed by our stations in Austin, TX (KASE 101) and San Antonio, TX (KJ97).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
